
Openstack Apply patch script will apply patches related to RPCore
to Openstack

Script will check the version of installed openstack over the machine
and then check if it has the patches for currently installed version.

If not, the script will exit.

Otherwise, it will apply the patch for provided argument.

e.g :
Following will apply the patches for controller
	bash ./Openstack_applyPatches.sh --controller

Following will apply the patches for compute node
	bash ./Openstack_applyPatches.sh --compute

